{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":549037,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"就看看呗","timestamp":1605243191,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":549038,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"你没有办法禁止别人洗，所以接受不了就别在洗衣机里洗","timestamp":1605243192,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":549040,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"还能仔细观察人家的袜子/内衣？","timestamp":1605243206,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":549041,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"另外可以善用搜索试试","timestamp":1605243219,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":549051,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"月经贴了，每隔一段时间就有类似的讨论。一句话结论：用好衣物消毒除菌剂，管别人洗啥的。","timestamp":1605243277,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":549052,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"垠神支持","timestamp":1605243284,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":549074,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我知道有衣物消毒液，但是真的不觉得埋汰吗……","timestamp":1605243589,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":549092,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 你有啥解决办法吗","timestamp":1605243881,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":549103,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"论埋汰程度，其实内衣＞外衣＞袜子……","timestamp":1605244133,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":549163,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"讲道理衣物消毒剂用多了也不好，而且其实并没有那么好的杀菌消毒效果。个人觉得集体生活空间，既然有人觉得介意，还是注意一点比较好（而且袜子内裤啥的和外衣混洗真的不卫生啊！）","timestamp":1605245015,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":549169,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"另外，解决不了问题就是提出问题的人有问题这种思路真的合理吗","timestamp":1605245104,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":549242,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"其实很多人这么做就是因为懒","timestamp":1605246096,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":549253,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"加消毒液就没事啊，看看科普文？","timestamp":1605246252,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":549289,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Grace: 普及了衣服消毒液和烘干机的国家从来没听说过这个问题，上世纪九十年代的老友记里就有去公共洗衣房的一幕也没见要内衣不能放一起洗。","timestamp":1605246848,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":549297,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":114455,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Grace: 觉得滴露、威露士等牌子的杀菌消毒效果不好的话推荐购买拜尔的衣物除菌液。","timestamp":1605246944,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":5,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":114455,"reply":15,"tag":null,"text":"想知道大家怎么看待用公共洗衣机洗袜子/内衣呢？qwq","timestamp":1605243144,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782643,"url":"","vote":{}}}